{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Story Background:</h2>The world has been tainted by a corrupting force of \u201cnoise\u201d. Those who are exposed to it might become manic, restless, and even transform into monsters.<br>At the same time, people have discovered that electronic music can resist this transformation and restore people's sanity.<br>Now, a group of exceptional teenagers will embark on a journey to vanquish the noise and restore peace by utilizing the power of electronic music.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321210/extras/1e.png?t=1683859322\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Experience different careers:</h2>The Early Access version contains three careers - Tachi Warrior, Gunner, and Boxer. Each of them has different talents and skills and possesses both \u201cCommon\u201d and \u201cNeon\u201d forms, creating different combat experience.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321210/extras/2.png?t=1683859322\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Free Combinations of Builds:</h2>Apart from the 7 factions of Builds in the game, we have &quot;Rhapsody&quot; for attack and skill form transformation, a more flexible in-game Build system called &quot;Rhythm Launchpad&quot;, and a challenging gameplay mode named \u201cSchrodinger's Noise\u201d that involves both attribute boosts and debuffs. By mixing these various Build systems, players can enjoy exciting linking reactions and expeirence unique battles.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321210/extras/3.gif?t=1683859322\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Random Combinations Battlefields:</h2>Based on the random battlefield design in the 3D side-scrolling Roguelite games, we are presenting you REAL random elements including random events &quot;Blake's Shop&quot; - players will randomly gain a buff or debuff, &quot;Nightmare Speaker&quot; - timed challenges, and various fun mini-games. The game has over 400 battlefields, avoiding monotonous adventures.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321210/extras/5.gif?t=1683859322\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Feel the Beats of Electronic Music:</h2>Players can find their own fighting paces following the &quot;electronic music&quot; in the game and decide whether to fight on the beats of the music. If they hit the beats, skills will have unexpected changes. When players enter a special status of &quot;Neonization&quot;, the BGM will be replaced with more intense electronic music. Put on your headphones, let music strike you in battle and feel the hype!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321210/extras/6.gif?t=1683859322\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Breakfree From the Iron Ocean","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2321210/bbc0f8837b340e2f31a375154b688aafd74cdcf0.jpg"},{"name":"Across the Snowfield","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2321210/bbc0f8837b340e2f31a375154b688aafd74cdcf0.jpg"},{"name":"Conqueror On Top","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2321210/bbc0f8837b340e2f31a375154b688aafd74cdcf0.jpg"},{"name":"Show Me Your Money","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2321210/da685f508ff8f48ad82c26924f58a85511e20301.jpg"},{"name":"I Am The Storm That Is Approaching","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2321210/4c320407b1395880a93fb4d0cc77ddab72f5c45e.jpg"},{"name":"Power Speaks For Itself","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2321210/b8743e295d0a24e6f417a86b500e96c99a36810b.jpg"},{"name":"Lord Of Ashes","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2321210/e6f8a29bf5